{"tid":1675627,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警察學院警長涉訛騙30名學警25萬元　廉署落案控四罪","createTime":"2019-10-26T04:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T05:00:05.000Z","uid":6261,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9b3196c537487a0ba93eea630ee4f8ac138cae5a","tid":1675627,"uid":6261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:30:41.000Z","msg":"廉政公署今日（25日）落案起訴一名警長，控告他涉嫌在香港警察學院監督一班30名受訓警員時，收受利益、公職人員行為失當及欺騙該等受訓警員，涉款共25萬元。被告於案發時為警長，駐守警察學院操練及槍械訓練組，是其中一班的副班主任，負責步操訓練、紀律及行政。其中案情指，被告涉嫌虛假地向30名受訓警員表示，各人均須支付6000元購買上一班受訓警員留下的多項文具及設備，以及合共6萬元租用專業設備製作紀念相簿。被告將於下星期二（29日）在東區裁判法院應訊，以待案件轉介區域法院答辯。"},{"pid":"740fac2b9ad06e1c79070fbac990a72fff68a4a9","tid":1675627,"uid":59289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:31:39.000Z","msg":"自己友都㩒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c140e7c8a2ef4156de7bb411e67de40d8854ae51","tid":1675627,"uid":100934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93bb6c0ba826fdfc53ce5aca512b3af48420893","tid":1675627,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"屌 仲有天理既？<br />\n散仔主席發起圍ICAC未？"},{"pid":"5d7b3c894f2f4e83a6748f57985103e18d67d0fc","tid":1675627,"uid":19984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:33:58.000Z","msg":"我宣布，十點鐘鳩嗌，正式回歸！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1674226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1674226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ctu4WC0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtu4WC0.jpg&h=0f6b4f14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRihxbm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRihxbm.jpg&h=cb7e0abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tQCx5yp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn